# Plugin Build

After every code change, run the Rojo build command to deploy the plugin.

The output filename **must match** the `name` field in `default.project.json`.

```bash
rojo build --plugin template-plugin.rbxmx
```

Rojo will handle placing the plugin in the correct location for your operating system.

Do this before any testing step. If Rojo is not installed, install it first:

```bash
aftman install
```
